&lt;p&gt;You will work closely with Design Directors, the ECD, and extended creative teams, building strategies that anchor distinctive, flexible brand expressions. Working across multiple projects at once, you’ll create roadmaps for brand systems that operate seamlessly across static, motion, and digital environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of a small London team, you’ll help set the standard for strategic quality and how brand work is made. The role suits someone who is globally minded, design-literate, and motivated by creating meaningful cultural connections.&lt;/p&gt;
