&lt;li&gt;Maintain a high bar for clarity, coherence, and craft across all strategic output&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to plan, build, and run collaborative client workshops, synthesizing stakeholder input and research into strategic platforms that guide design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Delivery and Collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead strategy across multiple projects from brief to delivery, balancing rigor, pace, and detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Design Directors, ECDs, and creative teams to develop strategy that informs creative expression and defines a distinctive position&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and deliver persuasive presentations tailored to diverse audiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to feedback constructively, iterating with intent and focus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
